Class ScannerImpl

    public final class ScannerImpl
extends Object
implements Scanner
     Scanner produces tokens of the following types:
 STREAM-START
 STREAM-END
 DIRECTIVE(name, value)
 DOCUMENT-START
 DOCUMENT-END
 BLOCK-SEQUENCE-START
 BLOCK-MAPPING-START
 BLOCK-END
 FLOW-SEQUENCE-START
 FLOW-MAPPING-START
 FLOW-SEQUENCE-END
 FLOW-MAPPING-END
 BLOCK-ENTRY
 FLOW-ENTRY
 KEY
 VALUE
 ALIAS(value)
 ANCHOR(value)
 TAG(value)
 SCALAR(value, plain, style)
 Read comments in the Scanner code for more details.
